  <title>TEXT Command (Core)</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">TEXT Command (Core)</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Syntax</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">TEXT</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">TO</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> &lt;VariableName&gt; [</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">ADDITIVE</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">] </text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> &#160; &#160; TextLines</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">ENDTEXT</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">&#32;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Arguments</para>
    <para styleclass="List">TextLines <tab /><text styleclass="Normal">Specifies text to assign to the variable VarName</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="List">TO &lt;<text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">VariableName&gt;</text><tab /><text styleclass="Normal">Specifies the variable name to use for passing the contents of the TEXT...ENDTEXT. This variable should be of type string, or should allow that a string can be added to it. It does not have to be a local variable, it can also be a field in the current class or an expression (someVar:SomeField)</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="List">ADDITIVE <tab /><text styleclass="Normal">Determines whether the contents of the TO variable are overwritten or added to existing contents. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">&#32;</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Example</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">FUNCTION</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> Start() </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">AS</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">VOID</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">LOCAL</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> cValue </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">AS</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">STRING</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">TEXT</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">TO</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> cValue</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">Line 1</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">Line 2</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">Line 3</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">ENDTEXT</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">? cValue</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">TEXT</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">TO</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> cValue </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">ADDITIVE</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">Line 4</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">Line 5</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">ENDTEXT</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">? cValue</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">RETURN</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The first time the variable will contain 3 lines of text delimited with CR/LF. The second time there will be 5 lines.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><br/><text styleclass="Code Example" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">The code produced by the compiler will somewhat look like this:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">FUNCTION</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> Start() </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">AS</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">VOID</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">LOCAL</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;"> cValue </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">AS</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">STRING</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">cValue := &quot;&quot;</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">cValue += &quot;Line 1&quot; + &#160;chr(13)+chr(10)</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">cValue += &quot;Line 2&quot; + &#160;chr(13)+chr(10)</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">cValue += &quot;Line 3&quot; + &#160;chr(13)+chr(10)</text><br/><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">? cValue</text><br/><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">cValue += &quot;Line 4&quot; + &#160;chr(13)+chr(10)</text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">cValue += &quot;Line 5&quot; + &#160;chr(13)+chr(10)</text><br/><br/><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">? cValue</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;">RETURN</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; color:#000000;">&#32;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1"></para>
